---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
import { config } from '../config';
---

<Layout title="About" description={`About ${config.author.name}`}>
  <header class="page-header">
    <span class="label">BIO</span>
    <h1>ABOUT</h1>
  </header>

  <article class="about">
    <section class="box intro">
      <p>
        I'm <strong>Jonathan D. Rhyne</strong>—a lawyer by training, an engineer at heart, and these days the co-founder & CEO of <a href="https://nutrient.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Nutrient.io</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        We build developer-first tools that let teams create, collaborate on, and automate documents across every major framework and device.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>THE STACK</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Nutrient Web Viewer & APIs</strong> — headless, high-fidelity document tooling for modern web apps</li>
        <li><strong>Low-code workflow automation</strong> — bringing citizen developers the same superpowers power users enjoy</li>
        <li><strong>AI document assistants</strong> — marrying LLMs with rock-solid SDKs</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>THE PRINCIPLES</h2>
      <div class="terminal">
        <div class="terminal-header">
          <span>EXEC: VALUES.CONFIG</span>
          <span>LOADED</span>
        </div>
        <div class="terminal-body">
          <p>01. Extreme ownership — low ego, high accountability</p>
          <p>02. Relentless curiosity — ship fast, learn faster</p>
          <p>03. Single-threaded focus — one priority at a time</p>
          <p>04. Bias for action — momentum beats perfection</p>
          <p>05. Radical candor — honest feedback fuels growth</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>BEYOND WORK</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>On the pitch — rec-league soccer</li>
        <li>Under dark skies — astrophotography with the kids</li>
        <li>At the NC coast — chasing sunrises</li>
        <li>Behind a Leica — minimalist B&W street shots</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="box cta">
      <p>
        > Building something that needs best-in-class document workflows?<br/>
        > <a href={`mailto:${config.social.email}`}>Ping me</a>—always up for chatting code, coffee, or clever growth loops.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    padding: var(--space-md) 0;
    border-bottom: var(--border);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    background: var(--black);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 0.2em 0.5em;
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .about {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .box {
    border: var(--border);
    padding: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .box p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .section h2 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .section ul {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .terminal {
    border: var(--border);
  }

  .terminal-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-sm);
    border-bottom: var(--border);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    background: var(--gray);
  }

  .terminal-body {
    padding: var(--space-sm);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .terminal-body p {
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .terminal-body p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .cta {
    background: var(--gray);
  }
</style>
